description: After completing level 1 you are ready to begin learning how Wing Chun can really be used. As before Level 2 Chum Kui (Sinking Bridge) training begins with a higher level of learning to know yourself. Master Wong will teach you to develop power and new skills to be used to search for your enemy find contact and destroy their defences. With Master Wong as your personal guide it has never been easier to take your Wing Chun to the next level.
title: Wing Chun Chum Kiu
